annotationA: CG5276, isoform A; Nucleoside-triphosphatase activity; nucleoside-diphosphatase activity; calcium ion binding
annotationB: UMP-CMP kinase; Catalyzes the phosphorylation of pyrimidine nucleoside monophosphates at the expense of ATP. Plays an important role in de novo pyrimidine nucleotide biosynthesis. Has preference for UMP and CMP as phosphate acceptors
